Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Eeehi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Buongiornooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.69,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Se riuscirò a essere splendida e avere successo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:58.50,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,come la idol Miki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.85,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,quando inizierò
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.40,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,la nuova scuola...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.50,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,potrò avere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,un sacco,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.44,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,ma proprio un sacco...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.27,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,di amiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Evviva!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:22.73,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ce l'ho fatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,È freddissima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:32.63,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Mi stavo chiedendo chi fosse appena caduto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Buongiorno, signor Taira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.08,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Come pensavo eri tu, Komichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:39.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ecco... io...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:42.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,mi stavo esercitando a nuotare vestita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:46.15,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Ti do un passaggio fino a casa. \NSali qui dietro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.61,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,So che ti hanno presa alla scuola media \Ndove hai fatto l'esame di ammissione.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sì! L'Accademia Roubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.60,main,Akebi,0000,0000,0000,,È una scuola privata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.36,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Dicono sia una scuola difficile. \NCi è andata tua madre, giusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:03.08,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sì. Per questo sono così felice \Nche mi abbiano accettata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.82,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Vedo! Vedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mi han detto che in tutte le classi\N ci sono più di dieci studentesse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Non riesco proprio a immaginarlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.70,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Alla scuola elementare Futaba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.90,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,sei sempre stata l'unica in classe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.94,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Sono contento per te!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Già!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:26.00,sign_3383_32_Akebi_s_Sailor_U,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(70,100,73,100)\fad(2156,1)\fsp.5\t(1,2156,\fsp0)}Akebi's Sailor Uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.38,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Grazieee!
