Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.76,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,La cena di congratulazioni è pronta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.60,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Hai due tuorli!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.25,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kao, hai sentito cos'è successo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.10,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Le giacche sono carine, vero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ahia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,P-Perché l'hai fatto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.21,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Non ti piace più la divisa alla marinaretta\N che ti ha fatto mamma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Non ho detto questo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.32,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi, sei brutta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.93,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Sei una stupida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:46.73,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Aaah, ti ho detto che non è così!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mi piace, anzi l'adoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:56.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Però non voglio che tutte pensino che sono strana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.07,flashback,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Perché tu sei fantastica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.09,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Voglio essere splendida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:08.52,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,E poi voglio farmi tante amiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:13.59,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Se sarò l'unica con la marinaretta, \Nmi farò notare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.07,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,E se fosse la mia occasione?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.78,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.61,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Vai già via?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.90,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:55.80,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Sei sicura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Fiducia in me stessa e un bel sorriso, giusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.88,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,A più tardi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Vado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Op...là!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ohi, ohi... c'è mancato poco.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.96,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Non sono convinta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Però...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,sento di avere le idee un po' più chiare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Pronti...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Viaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ciliegi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.76,sign_24797_279_Roubai_Academy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay.2\move(475,275,475,-25)}Accademia \NRoubai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.98,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Forse... mi sono esaltata... un po' troppo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,È enorme! Sembra un vero e proprio castello!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sono arrivata per prima?
